## Summary
This documentation covers the Session Replay Browser SDK Plugin (@amplitude/plugin-session-replay-browser) for instrumenting session replay functionality on sites already using Amplitude Browser SDK 2, including installation, configuration options like sampleRate and privacyConfig, DOM capture mechanics, data masking, and integration with the Unified SDK.

